Articles.Content:
I have just tried to install Kerbal Konstructs and KerbinSide Remastered but when I load the game the Buildings dont show but the section in difficukty options does.

Anybody know whats happening?

Did you have all the dependencies installed? Module manager? Outdating mods? Incompatible versions?

Logs and screenshots will help.

Edited July 17, 2018 by Xd the great

Yes just realised that the mod's max ksp version was 1.4.3 and i was using 1.4.4 

So i "downdated" my ksp then tried to install it and it worked fine.
